      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super clean inside, and runs like an absolute dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, fun car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
