    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S features the robust 3.8L flat-six powerplant, delivering linear torque across the rev range. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from factory-spec PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and an upgraded short-throw shifter for precise engagement of the 6-speed manual transaxle. Recent service includes a preventive IMS bearing retrofit and a full cooling system refresh. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with age, the mechanical integrity is excellent, with a clean DME report showing no over-revs in ranges 3-6. This is a driver-focused example with a functional limited-slip differential and crisp throttle response, ready for spirited canyon carving or weekend track duty.",
